        "Bonita Springs": "Okay so I have to tell you about my day because I literally cannot make this stuff up.  We showed up to a home inspection in Bonita Springs and the sellers were still there. Like fully home. One of them decided mid inspection was the perfect time to hop in the shower. 🚿  I promise you real estate in Southwest Florida keeps me on my toes every single day.  But here is the thing. My job is to protect my buyers no matter what chaos is happening around us. We smiled, we pivoted, and we got through an amazing inspection thanks to the most patient inspector on the planet.  Bonita Springs is one of the most competitive markets in Florida right now and you need someone in your corner who can handle literally anything.  Are you thinking about buying in Bonita Springs this year and want an agent who stays calm when things get wild?",
        "Lehigh Acres": "You literally cannot make this stuff up. We showed up to a home inspection in Lehigh Acres and the sellers decided it was the perfect time to hop in the shower. Like full on running water, the whole thing.  But here is the thing about Lehigh Acres real estate right now. Things get weird. Deals get complicated. Unexpected stuff happens constantly. The agent who wins for their client is the one who stays calm, smiles, and figures it out on the fly.  We pivoted. We laughed about it later. And honestly we got a great inspection report out of the whole situation.  Shoutout to my inspector for being an absolute legend about the whole thing.  This market keeps me on my toes every single day and I would not trade it for anything.  Are you thinking about buying in Lehigh Acres and wondering what the process actually looks like behind the scenes?",
