        "Lehigh Acres": "Did you know there's a specific day of the week that's BETTER to list your Lehigh Acres home than any other day? It's Thursday. When you list on Thursday, the MLS gives you two full weeks of new listing status. Buyers see \"new\" and they get excited. That's leverage.  And right now in Lehigh Acres, homes priced RIGHT are still seeing multiple offers. This week alone my buyers competed on homes with six plus offers.  But here's the real talk. If your home is sitting with zero offers, it's overpriced. Period. Today's buyers are doing their homework. They know every sale on your street. They are NOT overpaying.  Great marketing helps. Good videos help. But nothing out markets a bad price. Price it right, show it clean, have a strong negotiator in your corner and you will win.  Are you thinking about selling your Lehigh Acres home this year?",
        "Punta Gorda": "Did you know there's one specific day of the week that gets your home MORE attention on the MLS than any other day? It's Thursday. When you list on a Thursday in Punta Gorda, the MLS gives you two full weeks of \"new listing\" status. Buyers see that and get excited. That's just free leverage.  Now here's the real talk. If your home is sitting here in Punta Gorda and you're not getting offers, it's probably overpriced. Buyers in this market are doing their homework. They know every comp from Burnt Store Marina to Punta Gorda Isles. They are NOT overpaying.  Homes priced right are still getting multiple offers right now. I've seen it happen this week alone. Great price plus great showing experience equals buyers competing FOR you.  Equity isn't real until a buyer hands you a check.  So what's your biggest question about pricing your Punta Gorda home to actually sell?",
