      caption: "Walnut Creek just made history.  The highest residential sale ever recorded in this city. Ever. Right here in Northgate. Sold in 48 hours.  And people still sleep on Walnut Creek. Let us fix that.  Fun fact most people don’t know: Walnut Creek used to literally be called “Nuts Creek” when the first American settler arrived in 1849. Today that same city just broke its own real estate record. That’s a glow up.  This is a city with 23 distinct neighborhoods. Each one different. All of them desirable. And Northgate sits at the top of that list for a reason. A community where 73% of residents are executives and professionals. Where families move in and never leave. Where kids grow up, go to college, and come back to raise their own. That’s not a coincidence. That’s a culture.  And the city surrounding it?  · Mount Diablo State Park at your door · Top ranked schools in California · 30 minutes to San Francisco on BART · More open space per capita than any city in the state · Over 120 restaurants downtown  Stereo 41. LITA. Telefèric Barcelona. Original Joe’s. Va de Vi. Thai Torsap. The dining scene alone would make a foodie relocate.  Nordstrom. Alo. Lululemon. Vuori. @skims opening soon. RH Gallery arriving in 2026. This is not a suburb. This is a destination.  The wellness culture here is real. Barry’s Bootcamp just opened. Life Time is here. Club Studio. Solidcore. SoulCycle. The people of Walnut Creek move with intention.  Summers look like Art and Wine Festivals drawing 40,000 people, outdoor concerts at Broadway Plaza, Walnut Creek Uncorked, and Oktoberfest in the streets. This city has a pulse that most of the Bay Area hasn’t caught onto yet.  Kiana and I walked through this record breaking estate and filmed everything. Watch it.  This is the market we live in every single day. At every price point. And if you’re ready to make your move in the Bay Area we are the call you make first.  DM us. Let’s talk.  Jorge Martinez 📱 510.600.4359 DRE 02133848 | eXp Realty  Kiana Clay 📱 925.818.8687 DRE 02058272 | eXp Realty  Listing courtesy of @angieclay with Dudum Real Estate.  #WalnutCreek #BayAreaRealEstate #LuxuryRealEstate #NorCalRealEstate #NorthgateWalnutCreek",
